headline: Henry Schein (HSIC) Margin Improvement Challenges Bearish Profitability Narrative After Five-Year Earnings Decline
summary: Henry Schein (HSIC) delivered earnings growth of 24.4% over the past year, a notable change compared to its five-year average decline of 10% per year. Net profit margins improved to 3%, up from 2.5% last year, and while projected annual earnings growth sits at 15.89%, which is a touch below the broader US market’s 16%, it still signals steady momentum for the company. For investors, these results point to improving profitability and a shift towards more favorable outcomes, even as revenue...

headline: VideaHealth and Henry Schein One Launch the Impact Panel, Bringing AI-Driven Patient Education to Dentrix and Dentrix Ascend
summary: BOSTON, November 05, 2025--VideaHealth, the leading dental AI platform, in collaboration with Henry Schein One, today announced the launch of the Impact Panel, a new enhancement within the Detect AI experience for Dentrix® and Dentrix Ascend® users. This product enhancement integrates VideaHealth’s real-time AI findings and patient education tools directly into Henry Schein One’s imaging workflows, enabling clinicians to communicate more clearly and guide patients toward confident treatment disc
